descriptionHtml:
This mod adds some random stuff. What stuff, you ask? Well, let me tell you!

- Shivs now deal 6 damage instead of 5
- Nazeem is re-named and also has a copy of Kolb and the Dragon in his inventory
- The Jarl of Whiterun now has a bottle of Skooma in his inventory
- Both volumes of The Lusty Argonian Maid now have values of 69
- There is a roll of paper missing from the basket in the mage's room in Dragonsreach
- Maybe a couple other things I forgot about
author: Me
